  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Database for management of climate adaptation information and data</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Indonesia, the statistical basis for the efficient use of climate adaptation information and the formulation of appropriate adaptation strategies were insufficient. There was a lack of scientific capacities as well as of human, financial and technical resources. Accordingly, the purpose of the project was to improve Indonesia&#x2019;s ability to adapt to climate change impacts by means of an improved statistical basis and a standardised processing of data. A further goal of the project was to create an information management system to support planning, implementation and monitoring of adaptation measures.</narrative>
  </description>
